import React, { useState } from 'react' const App = () => { let [data,setdata]=useState({ FirstName:"", LastName:"", Emailaddress:"", Password:"" }) const InputEvent=(event)=>{ let {name,value}=event.target; setdata((previous)=>{ return{ ...previous, [name]:value } }) } const Formsubmit=(e)=>{ e.preventDefault(); alert(`name${data.fullname}`) } return ( <>
) } export default App
